{"tid":1467276,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【文宣組】拆掂今日機場事件的方法","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:11:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T18:01:56.000Z","uid":304510,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"59fb39514489865266d0c0ed236b1a1d9ed66284","tid":1467276,"uid":304510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:11:15.000Z","msg":"首先，前線做乜我都無條件支持，絕對不割蓆。但係但係而家我地需要爭取更多人支持，所以唔可以俾外界覺得示威者好暴力，因為無民意、外國輿論倒戈就一切收皮。至於我地自己做佐乜嘢自己心知就可以。<br />\n<br />\n文宣可以從以下方向解釋今日機場發生的事件：<br />\n【今日機場發生的所有衝突都是一個寫好的劇本】<br />\n琴日和平佔領機場的行動非常成功，無警察、無塞旅客、無受傷、無流血、無捉鬼，一切都好和平<br />\n因為香港國際機場係香港重要樞紐，警察不可以隨便在裡面開槍驅趕，所以今日就寫一個劇本來抹黑示威者<br />\n<br />\n琴日萬人集會，<br />\n琴日完全發生過堵塞旅客的情況<br />\n琴日即使發現有便衣都無人上前捉鬼，並與之衝突過去<br />\n兩個幾月不會有示威者阻止救援、辱罵記者<br />\n今日係機場一早就捉到幾個大陸公安，係背包搜到長棍<br />\n夜晚一捉就捉到個大陸官媒《環球時報》記者，然後係背包搜到件黑幫藍Tee，示威者仲要係所有鏡頭下面打人，阻止急救員同醫生急救，阻止記者拍攝。睇返直播個 「記者」仲要不停挑釁示威者話支持警察<br />\n<br />\n如果你係鬼會唔會咁容易穿煲呀，會唔會帶咁多證明自己係鬼既野呀。<br />\n所以今日就係一個抹黑刻意示威者既劇本，目的係要令改變輿論，可以製造示威者暴力的形象。<br />\n<br />\n大家集思廣益下文宣可以點樣寫。核爆炸死埋我都唔割！！！！！！"},{"pid":"5bf04fd8e4bfab8549f012ffaaa2f24486c97ecf","tid":1467276,"uid":285481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:12:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7C2rZZK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7C2rZZK.jpg&h=f803e7b2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XesjAx4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXesjAx4.jpg&h=881bc552&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"173ddfa8baafb21c381b8cff943ee804e65433fe","tid":1467276,"uid":304510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:15:57.000Z","msg":"自推 <br />\n不割蓆"},{"pid":"85800fdbc7f8f6c73b9f90967119930d1abf7d75","tid":1467276,"uid":304510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:16:16.000Z","msg":"自推2<br />\n不割蓆"},{"pid":"6584f39a15b4c622b745067f5f3e99c196c39c24","tid":1467276,"uid":304510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:17:16.000Z","msg":"自推3<br />\n不割蓆"},{"pid":"e10f0baf96745eb5950b980f4623e0f3bc09f0d6","tid":1467276,"uid":304510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:17:38.000Z","msg":"自推4<br />\n不割蓆"},{"pid":"7faa56f01c49fbafa195a4451d7f4588a72270ca","tid":1467276,"uid":304510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:18:32.000Z","msg":"自推3<br />\n不割蓆"},{"pid":"c981afc52c7ac338942c320cd575cd9195e72868","tid":1467276,"uid":304510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:20:33.000Z","msg":"自推6<br />\n不割蓆"},{"pid":"62d8a1435b566dbac1baf7c74cdff6d853e4c6d2","tid":1467276,"uid":304510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:22:04.000Z","msg":"自推7<br />\n不割蓆"},{"pid":"c3734a02318221f7e46307a2826419115474627e","tid":1467276,"uid":304510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:23:06.000Z","msg":"自推8<br />\n不割蓆"},{"pid":"176bb5345e604d48cb37005d277a6ea7c0b80342","tid":1467276,"uid":304510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:24:03.000Z","msg":"自推9<br />\n不割蓆"},{"pid":"c841bd8c071dacc3baf1a868c00241901e7117a9","tid":1467276,"uid":304510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:24:51.000Z","msg":"自推10<br />\n不割蓆"},{"pid":"c9e64817a53296b17865f35933e6edd313b48dfe","tid":1467276,"uid":224942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:26:15.000Z","msg":"推！<br />\n<br />\n想繼續發夢 各位要有思想上既進化！<br />\n<br />\n不割席 不分化<br />\n<br />\n！！！不要被人有機可乘！！！<br />\n<br />\n依兩日機場其實達到既效果好大，影響好深遠！<br />\n<br />\n唔需要理會啲鬼！！"},{"pid":"58ee58c6f85b8605212d4eb1cf7503023c804b12","tid":1467276,"uid":76867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:27:27.000Z","msg":"咁拆都係治標不治本<br />\n因為日後會有更多同樣甚至更激烈情況發生<br />\n未諗到點拆<br />\n照幫你推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf9fbf7abbd23c8253f84ec07f9ed6ac9f9d2c01","tid":1467276,"uid":285481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:29:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qpBgCSS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqpBgCSS.jpg&h=d866058e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0886Z6d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0886Z6d.jpg&h=d6540e13&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cfbcc832dd84ec8c8899ca022ad57d4bdef6237d","tid":1467276,"uid":300697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:29:55.000Z","msg":"如需國際輿論協助抗爭，千萬不要再 Block T2！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港國際機場客運量極大，T2 的狹小不能夠處理一半以上的乘客出入境。Delay 的班機每天一定過百。大量旅客不能順暢登機，飛機好難順利凖時起飛。佔用了停機位，抵港航班延誤是難以避免的。<br />\n<br />\n只佔據T1，旅客一方面覺得有登機的機會，但另一方面需要付出額外的時間代價。他們是會覺得港府無能力與市民對話解決紛爭，而不是覺得示威者暴力。<br />\n<br />\n香港不同其他地方，我們只有一個國際機場。如果我們將它完全癱瘓，只會令許多外國人有家歸不得而對示威者有極大的抱怨。西方國家領袖都是很著緊輿論和選票。如果香港示威者的行為損害到他們國民的權利，他們不會再支持香港示威者。<br />\n<br />\n走到來機場這步棋，已經是最後的對決。8.11 警方是錯得離譜，國際輿論全部都指責警方的暴行。要蓋過一單黑材料，最容易的方法是製造一單更大的黑材料。今天示威者比較霸道的行為完全是正中下懷。<br />\n<br />\n你可能覺得我是P 牌無資格講野，但是千萬不要忘記我們的行動是代表全香港相信抗爭的人。請大家一定要用理智思考如何處理這件事情，不要起於情緒化。<br />\n<br />\n如果你看過這篇文章，無論如何請幫推和 re post , 我絕對不介意你們自行修改，改成你們的意見。<br />\n<br />\n大家加油！"},{"pid":"ae96dfe003951b45b24c4b2c32bf449d2c52d544","tid":1467276,"uid":304510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58ee58c6f85b8605212d4eb1cf7503023c804b12","tid":1467276,"uid":76867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:27:27.000Z","msg":"咁拆都係治標不治本<br />\n因為日後會有更多同樣甚至更激烈情況發生<br />\n未諗到點拆<br />\n照幫你推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:47:54.000Z","msg":"發動道歉運動<br />\n所有暴力行為都係警方煽動（唔係想無視前線手足付出，只係想爭取更多民意）<br />\n我好想大家可以成功呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63a375aeec3bab5ff19e466a66196336db91569f","tid":1467276,"uid":128307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:54:49.000Z","msg":"照推！<br />\n希望大家有時間都睇睇我嘅建議<br />\n<br />\n[url]緊急！各位勇武派手足麻煩入一入嚟 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1465294\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1465294</a> - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區[/url]"},{"pid":"29509b301205618369d94b01705a02118e213b43","tid":1467276,"uid":110579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:01:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/67950496_2529764247080173_6460197950730534912_n.jpg?_nc_cat=111&amp;_nc_oc=AQkvR_RT2WizLB7N800wXdcAiY_aUAprRHPaZqV55N3f9ZB4Pbf6GUcTu8ovlhuVENg&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg3-1.xx&amp;oh=dba94cbfd41b8b4577b4fbbcffc9be29&amp;oe=5DCB7A12\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F67950496_2529764247080173_6460197950730534912_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D111%26_nc_oc%3DAQkvR_RT2WizLB7N800wXdcAiY_aUAprRHPaZqV55N3f9ZB4Pbf6GUcTu8ovlhuVENg%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg3-1.xx%26oh%3Ddba94cbfd41b8b4577b4fbbcffc9be29%26oe%3D5DCB7A12&h=6f4dfc03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nfb見到，原post:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/flyagainla/posts/2529730620416869\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fflyagainla%2Fposts%2F2529730620416869&d=4IYAvm%2F2ThyFbSIl4Y3IjyWHaP8IcnP89ZPrefCyuoo%3D&h=9ada67a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/flyagainla/posts/2529730620416869</a>"}]}